Package org.apache.jena.ext.io.github.galbiston.expiring_map

Class ExpiringMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<K,V>
org.apache.jena.ext.io.github.galbiston.expiring_map.ExpiringMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - Key entry object.
V - Value entry object.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ConcurrentMap<K,V>, Map<K,V>
public class ExpiringMap<K,V> extends ConcurrentHashMap<K,V>
Expiring Map for storage of entries which expire if unused for a period of time.
Size of map, duration until expiry and frequency of cleaning can all be controlled.
